{"tid":392833,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[中史台] 有無人覺得三國時代呢一百年間 最撚仆街果個叫姜維？","createTime":"2017-09-08T18:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T09:15:48.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d3817672392c02924f3f49bc90d6c325270c52","tid":392833,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:11:37.000Z","msg":"魏國出身,諸葛亮打到來就投降獻城 <br />\n之後仲積極打返舊主魏國,十二次北伐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打到勞民傷材 係蜀地變到神憎鬼厭<br />\n最尾蜀國投降 d百姓以為從此安享太平<br />\n點知佢又走去策反鍾會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令益州再一次捲入兵連禍結之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957d9619891993606d4306ccce76eaa73d66a52b","tid":392833,"uid":137768,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:26:37.000Z","msg":"如果搞到有兵禍就係仆街嘅話<br />\n咁所有三國出名嘅人物都係仆街啦"},{"pid":"37c5fd024861a01cd46074abbf8ebc0628e84d5c","tid":392833,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果搞到有兵禍就係仆街嘅話<br />\n咁所有三國出名嘅人物都係仆街啦</blockquote><br />\n姜維根本就同諸葛恪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好大喜功 窮兵黷武"},{"pid":"f62a7075b09104a5231687dc2537a04d52527818","tid":392833,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T23:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果搞到有兵禍就係仆街嘅話<br />\n咁所有三國出名嘅人物都係仆街啦</blockquote><br />\n姜維根本就同諸葛恪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好大喜功 窮兵黷武</blockquote><br />\n唔keep住北伐既話<br />\nn年後<br />\n蜀國仲係5-6萬 魏國就會發展到5-60萬<br />\n到時統戰就如踩死隻蟻一樣"},{"pid":"1992b0c6c63957ccd55bd5f462d07b3dcf08944a","tid":392833,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T00:02:48.000Z","msg":"其實去到後期（蜀吳反面之後），有冇試過蜀吳兩個一齊去打"},{"pid":"3fd4ad13bde3fe17771ae1f64f8696dd8c48950e","tid":392833,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實去到後期（蜀吳反面之後），有冇試過蜀吳兩個一齊去打</blockquote><br />\n多數吳國響應蜀國北伐<br />\n吳蜀反面之後極速frd返喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67470b6929a14790620cda728b0a41a884ae50da","tid":392833,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實去到後期（蜀吳反面之後），有冇試過蜀吳兩個一齊去打</blockquote><br />\n夷陵後關係名存實亡啦<br />\n兩邊無打起黎only 枉論合作。。"},{"pid":"2db1cd596a9f34f9d9ae6e0ac5e1f4ac069aa6ee","tid":392833,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"姜維既北伐係上去搶人地國民補落蜀國到 唔係志在霸人地既土 請問你識唔撚識嫁？ 佢俾人憎 係因為後主信個垃圾咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50bf597034fa3154bf37401b2ca718669687cea","tid":392833,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T07:03:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"415a874c9e087d8c6f26269cf0489a1bf184cdb1","tid":392833,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"呢句真 我依家就屌撚死你個仆街仔"}]}